      "honorificSuffix": "CPA",
      "jobTitle": "Founder",
      "description": "Tyler Wilcox, CPA is the founder of Velu and has more than 15 years of accounting experience, including over a decade serving nonprofit organizations through nonprofit accounting, financial reporting, Form 990 preparation, federal tax compliance, consulting, and audit-related experience. He is a Certified Public Accountant, QuickBooks ProAdvisor Level 2, and holder of the AICPA Nonprofit Level 1 Certificate.",
